全球同此宅，Steam同时在线人数首次突破2000万大关。
At the same time, Steam is breaking the 20 million mark for the first time.
嘤肉卫星。
Twist satellites.
趣闻。
Interesting news.
4天前。
Four days ago.
人们在家里找到了新乐趣。
People find new joys at home.
。
.
就在前晚，Steam平台上的同时在线用户再次创下新高，达到了史无前例的2000万人（准确来讲，是20313457）。
Just the night before, contemporaneous online users on the Steam platform hit an all-time high of 20 million (20313457 to be precise).
。
.
最近一段日子，细心的朋友应该已经发现Steam平台上同时在线，以及正在游戏中的用户数量有了明显增长。
These days, observant friends should have noticed a marked increase in the number of users on the Steam platform, both online and in-game.
就在上个月，Steam在线用户刚刚突破了1900万大关，这也是自2018年1月以来，同时在线的最高人数。
Just last month, Steam online users passed the 19 million mark, the highest number online since January 2018.
。
.
在两个月内接连打破在线人数记录，此前罕有发生，虽然目前还没有明确的证据和统计，但不可否认的是，本次新型冠状病毒疫情势必在一定程度上影响了人们的生活习惯，也间接导致了世界范围内“宅经济”的发展。
Although there is no clear evidence and statistics, it is undeniable that this new coronavirus epidemic will affect people's living habits to a certain extent and indirectly lead to the development of the "house economy" in the world.
。
.
疫情当前，各国人民都尽量减少了出行计划，对于被迫宅在家里的人们来说，游戏自然成为了最好的消遣形式。
The epidemic is occurring at a time when people around the world have minimized travel plans and games have naturally become the best form of recreation for people forced to stay at home.
在昨日2000万人在线的高峰时段，有近620万玩家正在游戏中，而高居榜首的依旧是大家熟悉的面孔：。
Nearly 6.2 million players were playing at the peak of yesterday's 20m online session, with familiar faces still at the top of the list.
除了Steam这个中国玩家熟知的游戏平台。
In addition to Steam, a well-known game platform for Chinese players.
隔壁主机区的Xbox也适时发布了号召大家少出门，一起宅在家里玩游戏的推文：。
The Xbox, next door to the main frame, also issued a tweet calling on everyone to go out less and stay at home playing games together.
Xbox的总裁Phil Sprncer也转发了该推特，并激动地表示：“为自己身为游戏行业一员感到自豪，这个行业能在特殊时期给人们安全地提供快乐。
Phil Sprncer, president of Xbox, also tweeted and excitedly said: "I'm proud to be part of the game industry, which can provide people with security in special times.
。
.
也许玩家们都听到了Xbox官方的号召，同样在前几日，Xbox live的服务器也因为大量用户同时在线而导致瘫痪，不仅多人游戏受到影响，连基本的购买、下载等操作也无法实现：。
Players may have heard the official Xbox call, and the Xbox Live server was paralyzed by a flood of concurrent users, affecting not only multiplayer games but also basic purchases and downloads:
这个故障在昨日凌晨终于得到了部分修复。
The malfunction was finally partially repaired in the early hours of yesterday.
除了游戏行业，宅在家里的年轻人也间接促使某些大家“喜闻乐见”的影视公司推出了“宅男福利”。
In addition to the game industry, the home-based youth also indirectly prompted some of the "popular" film and television companies to introduce "Mansion male welfare."
。
.
日本著名成人影视公司“SOD”就在全民抗疫的关键时期免费开放了旗下200部制作精良的教学影片，其中也包括了人气很高的“VR系列”，只要你注册成为SOD会员，即可免费观看这些影片直到3月结束。
Japan's best-known adult film company SOD opened its 200 well-made educational films free of charge during the critical period of the national epidemic, including the popular "VR Series," which can be viewed free of charge until March, as long as you register as SOD members.
。
.
不知道是为了避免人们因出门而感染病毒，还是想间接降低宅男们的免疫力。
Do not know in order to avoid people out of the virus, or to indirectly reduce the mansion men's immunity.
成人网站Pornhub也不约而同地为刚刚面临封城的意大利人民准备了一个月的免费会员套餐，以此帮助那些可能按捺不住的单身男女们：。
Pornhub, the adult Web site, also helped potentially irresistible single men and women by preparing a free one-month membership package for Italians who had just faced closure.
无论是游戏用户的激增还是成人影视的官方福利，都是为了给无法出门的人们带来快乐，就像SOD在该活动上特别强调的：“希望大家保持正确的生活作息下，给每一位用户带来一点笑容就够了。
Both the proliferation of game users and the official benefits of adult film and television are meant to bring happiness to people who cannot leave their homes, as SOD emphasized at the event: "I hope everyone lives right and gives everyone a smile.
”。
"
